OL,3,CDisabled politician blasts 'shambles'
OL,4,Cafter Aer Lingus plane left without him
OL,6,FA disabled MLA has described a
OL,7,F"shambles" after being unable to board
OL,8,Fa plane.
OL,10,FAndy Allen had been travelling from
OL,11,FBirmingham home to Belfast at the
OL,12,Fweekend when his Aer Lingus plane left
OL,13,Fwithout him.
OL,15,FHe has contended the assistance he
OL,16,Fneeds to board the plane on his
OL,17,Fwheelchair did not come.
OL,19,FThere were widespread expressions of
OL,20,Fsolidarity with Mr Allen at the
OL,21,FStormont Assembly on Monday.
