OL,3,CDisabled politician blasts 'shambles'
OL,4,Cafter Aer Lingus plane left without him
OL,6,FHe missed asking the first question to
OL,7,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill during
OL,8,Fquestions to the Executive Office.
OL,10,FMs O'Neill described the UUP MLA as
OL,11,Fhaving been "stranded at an airport in
OL,12,FEngland due to not having accessible
OL,13,Fservices".
OL,15,F"Airlines and every other service need
OL,16,Fto do better to support those people
OL,17,Fwith additional needs," she told MLAs.
