OL,3,CDisabled politician blasts 'shambles'
OL,4,Cafter Aer Lingus plane left without him
OL,6,FEarlier, during Members' Statements,
OL,7,FUUP MLA Robbie Butler said it was
OL,8,F"quite frankly outrageous that in
OL,9,F2024, basic rights and access that
OL,10,Fmost of us take for granted are still
OL,11,Fdenied to disabled individuals".
OL,13,FHe added: "This is a stain on those
OL,14,Fwho profit from their activities
OL,15,Fwhilst neglecting the responsibility
OL,16,Fto all of their customers."
OL,18,FTaking to the social media network X
OL,19,Fon Sunday, Mr Allen branded the
OL,20,Fincident as a "shambles".
